OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FHundreds of devotees flocked to a
OL,7,Ftemple in Kent to see a rare Hindu
OL,8,Fceremony take place.
OL,10,FThe Medway Hindu Mandir revealed a
OL,11,Fnumber of its new deities to its
OL,12,Fcongregation for the first time in a
OL,13,FMurti Sthapana ceremony, otherwise
OL,14,Fknown as the placing of the statues.
OL,16,FThe Mandir was already home to a deity
OL,17,Fthat arrived 30 years ago, but more
OL,18,Fwere unveiled to guests from behind a
OL,19,Fcurtain - including Ram Darbar, Radha
OL,20,FKrishna and Lord Shiva.
