OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FThey were introduced to people in a
OL,7,FPrana Pratishtha ceremony, which means
OL,8,Fthe bringing of life to the deities.
OL,10,FThe room was filled with excitement
OL,11,Fwhen the Murtis were unveiled, with
OL,12,Fpeople singing and dancing in
OL,13,Fcelebration.
OL,15,FThe temple has been serving Medway
OL,16,Fsince 1978, and organisers say it was
OL,17,Fthe biggest event in the Mandir's
OL,18,Fhistory.
