OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FGeneral Secretary of the Medway Hindu
OL,7,FMandir, Ajay Attra said: "The beauty
OL,8,Fabout the Murti Sthapana ceremony is
OL,9,Fthat it involves everybody.
OL,11,F"People have donated the food for
OL,12,Ftoday and people have donated the
OL,13,Fclothes.
OL,15,F"Murti worship is a form of worship
OL,16,Fwhich allows people to create a
OL,17,Fphysical connection with God. It's a
OL,18,Fvisual connection.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
