OL,6,F"The deities that you see in front are
OL,7,Fyou are not just statues, we believe
OL,8,Fthey are God manifested within those
OL,9,Fstatues.
OL,11,F"People even say that the deities
OL,12,Finstalled within the temples, they
OL,13,Fwill listen and answer your prayers."
OL,15,FThe three-day ceremony took three
OL,16,Fyears of planning and it is believed
OL,17,Faround 500 people attended the Mandir
OL,18,Ffor the ritual in a day filled with
OL,19,Fprayers, hymns, and offerings.
