OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FMany wore yellow to the occasion which
OL,7,Fis an auspicious colour in Hinduism.
OL,9,FAttendee Akhil Bhargava said his
OL,10,Ffamily were involved in the
OL,11,F"cleansing" of the Murtis (statues).
OL,13,F"When they've been welcomed into the
OL,14,FMandir, you have a lot of different
OL,15,Fthings which you have to do to the
OL,16,FMurtis, whether it's bathing them or
OL,17,Fclothing them," he said.
