OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FThe statues were adorned in regal
OL,7,Fattire, including crowns, jewellery
OL,8,Fand clothing. It is believed the
OL,9,Fdifferent deities each offer Hindus
OL,10,Fdifferent lessons.
OL,12,FAkhil added that practising the
OL,13,Freligion is something that has been
OL,14,Fpassed down from his grandparents.
OL,16,FHe said: "In this day and age, I
OL,17,Fpersonally feel that practising
OL,18,Freligion is not something that's as
OL,19,Fbig as it was once before.
