OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,F"To see a community like ourselves
OL,7,Fcome together to celebrate this
OL,8,Foccasion, it's warming."
OL,10,FShalini Vilas has been attending the
OL,11,Ftemple for the last 37 years, she
OL,12,Fsaid: "For me it's quite meaningful
OL,13,Fand to see so many people around here
OL,14,Ftoday has been really good."
OL,16,F"The people who actually come here,
OL,17,Fthey are part of me, we are part of
OL,18,Fthis family and it's like a sense of
OL,19,Fbelonging."
