OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FAs well as the ceremonial placement of
OL,7,Fthe deities in the temple, a fire
OL,8,Fceremony or 'Havan' also took place.
OL,10,FThe temple said it symbolised
OL,11,Fpurification, not just of the air, but
OL,12,Fof the mind and soul.
OL,14,FThe consecration ceremony was also
OL,15,Fattended by the Mayor of Medway, Cllr
OL,16,FNina Gurung, who is the first female
OL,17,FMayor of Nepalese and British Gurkha
OL,18,Fheritage in the country - and Medway's
OL,19,Ffirst Buddhist Mayor.
