OL,3,CHundreds of devotees mark rare Hindu
OL,4,Cceremony at Medway temple
OL,6,FShe said: "Medway is a very very rich
OL,7,Ftapestry, consisting of more than 45
OL,8,Fdifferent community groups.
OL,10,F"I take my hat off to all the
OL,11,Fvisionary elders who came here in
OL,12,FMedway all those years ago and felt it
OL,13,Fwas important for them to establish
OL,14,Fthis Hindu temple.
OL,16,F"I could see that there were lots of
OL,17,Fnon-Hindu people as well who were
OL,18,Fwelcomed with open arms today. You
OL,19,Fknow we all come together to celebrate
OL,20,Feach other's diversity."
